   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>From Appianus to Choous, brick-maker, greeting. Give to Argaios, son of me, Phasganius, bricks to the number of one thousand, equal 1000.;(2nd hand) I have authorized this order.;(1st hand) Year 6, Pharmouthi 19</ab>
         </div>
